		<h5>Electricity, Water &amp; Rent</h5>
		<p>
			Electricity, depending on how it's contracted, is paid every one or two months.
			<br>
			Water is paid every three months.
			<br>
			Rent <strong>must</strong> be paid before the 5th of every month.
			<br><br>
			All of these are to be paid through the bank by transfer or you can set it up to be paid automatically (direct debit).
		</p>
